      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 62.7</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 62.7</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>雖有拱璧以先駟馬，不如坐進此道。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Therefore when the sovereign occupies his place as the Son of Heaven, and he has appointed his three ducal ministers, though (a prince) were to send in a round symbol-of-rank large enough to fill both the hands, and that as the precursor of the team of horses (in the court-yard), such an offering would not be equal to (a lesson of) this Dao, which one might present on his knees.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
