      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 62.9</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 62.9</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>不曰以求得，有罪以免邪？</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Was it not because it could be got by seeking for it, and the guilty could escape (from the stain of their guilt) by it?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
